m/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06174223/Era-in-box-630x420.jpg 630w\"></p><h3>Contact and Dealer Information</h3><p>Visit EXT USA <a href=\"https://extusa.bike/\">here</a> for more details. Through the website, the brand also welcomes dealer applications. For U.S.-based MTB riders, there’s never been a better time to jump on it. (So to speak.)</p></div></div>","author":"Sam Anderson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"0f07b909000b7a11b47dcef1b9b23a08e0354f1c317c3ff59c7412a02603f444","category":"Cycling"}